# Test: AssetEventsNotFullSale
# Purpose: Tests partial sales with capital returns and accumulation dividends
#          adjusting the Section 104 cost base
# Rules Tested: Section 104 Pooling, Capital Return (CAPRETURN), Accumulation
#               dividends (ACCUMULATION)
# Complexity: Medium
# Key Features: Two partial sales in different tax years, corporate-action pairs
#               between and after the sales
# Expected Outcome: 2019/20 gain £25 (first sale), 2020/21 gain £64.00 (second sale)
#
# Verification Status: Verified
# Verified By: Reconciled against golden output 2026-06-21
# Verification Notes: Matches tests/json/AssetEventsNotFullSale.json and
#                     tests/plain/AssetEventsNotFullSale.txt. Figures are exact under
#                     chronological replay: each disposal is priced off the pool as it
#                     stood on the disposal date, so the 2021-04-01 corporate actions
#                     do not leak back into the 2020-07-01 sale.
#
#   Buy 1: 2019-08-01, 10 @ £100 = £1,000.00
#   Pool: 10 shares, £1,000.00
#
#   Sell 5 @ £105 (2019-09-01):
#     Proceeds: 5 × £105 = £525.00
#     Allowable cost: 5/10 × £1,000.00 = £500.00
#     Gain: £525.00 - £500.00 = £25.00
#   Pool: 5 shares, £500.00
#
#   Buy 2: 2020-01-01, 10 @ £90 = £900.00
#   Pool: 15 shares, £1,400.00
#   2020-04-01 ACCUMULATION 15, £30 (raises pool cost): £1,400.00 + £30.00 = £1,430.00
#   2020-04-01 CAPRETURN 15, £50 (reduces pool cost):   £1,430.00 - £50.00 = £1,380.00
#   Pool: 15 shares, £1,380.00
#
#   Buy 3: 2020-06-01, 10 @ £80 = £800.00
#   Pool: 25 shares, £2,180.00  (avg £87.20/share)
#
#   Sell 5 @ £100 (2020-07-01):
#     Proceeds: 5 × £100 = £500.00
#     Allowable cost: 5/25 × £2,180.00 = £436.00
#     Gain: £500.00 - £436.00 = £64.00
#   Pool: 20 shares, £1,744.00
#
#   2021-04-01 ACCUMULATION 20, £40: £1,744.00 + £40.00 = £1,784.00
#   2021-04-01 CAPRETURN 10, £10:    £1,784.00 - £10.00 = £1,774.00
#   Final holding: 20 shares, £1,774.00 (avg £88.70/share)
#
2019-08-01 BUY FOOBAR 10 @ 100 FEES 0
2019-09-01 SELL FOOBAR 5 @ 105 FEES 0
2020-01-01 BUY FOOBAR 10 @ 90 FEES 0
2020-04-01 ACCUMULATION FOOBAR 15 TOTAL 30 TAX 0
2020-04-01 CAPRETURN FOOBAR 15 TOTAL 50 FEES 0
2020-06-01 BUY FOOBAR 10 @ 80 FEES 0
2020-07-01 SELL FOOBAR 5 @ 100 FEES 0
2021-04-01 ACCUMULATION FOOBAR 20 TOTAL 40 TAX 0
2021-04-01 CAPRETURN FOOBAR 10 TOTAL 10 FEES 0
